    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large liquor cabinets having spaces designed specifically for holding bottles of liquor, wine, glasses, other utensils, ice, and a shelf or surface needed for making and serving drinks. </Note_Text>
